data.description: Welcome to this cozy and inviting property located on a serene cul-de-sac. This well-maintained two bedroom and one bath home offers a spacious fenced backyard and an attached garage, built in 1981. There is a  charming rock wall wood stove that will keep you warm and toasty in the winter months. It is the perfect starter home or a great home for retirement. Located just a short distance from the convenience of town. Schedule an appointment today!
